<view class="screen" wx:if="{{profile}}">
  <view class="stack">
    <view class="hero-card membership-hero">
      <view class="stack-tight">
        <text class="eyebrow">会员中心</text>
        <text class="page-title">高手会员</text>
        <text class="page-subtitle" wx:if="{{fromQuota}}">
          今日免费轮次已用完，继续训练前需要开通会员。
        </text>
        <text class="page-subtitle" wx:else>
          会员版重点解决的是频次限制和反馈深度限制。
        </text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="plan-card membership-plan">
      <view class="row-between">
        <text class="section-title">连续包月</text>
        <text class="page-title membership-price">¥19</text>
      </view>
      <view class="stack-tight">
        <text class="section-copy">- 无限继续下一轮，不被 3 次免费额度拦截</text>
        <text class="section-copy">- 查看完整 AI 点评和细分评分</text>
        <text class="section-copy">- 历史记录可长期回看</text>
        <text class="section-copy">- 后续可接个性化词池推荐</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="upsell-card membership-note">
      <text class="section-title">开通后可获得</text>
      <text class="section-copy">
        无限训练轮次、完整 AI 点评拆解、更长历史记录以及后续的个性化词池。
      </text>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{profile.isMember}}" class="primary-button" bindtap="handleGoProfile">
      <text>已开通，回到我的</text>
    </view>
    <view wx:else class="primary-button" bindtap="handleOpenPay">
      <text>立即开通会员</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{showPaySheet}}" class="sheet-mask">
    <view class="sheet-panel">
      <view class="stack">
        <view class="stack-tight">
          <text class="section-title">确认支付</text>
          <text class="section-copy">表达高手会员｜连续包月 ¥19</text>
          <text class="section-copy muted">支付方式：微信支付</text>
        </view>

        <view class="status-row">
          <view class="status-chip status-chip--ink">
            <text>{{paymentState === 'processing' ? '支付处理中' : '待支付'}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="status-chip">
            <text>完整点评</text>
          </view>
          <view class="status-chip">
            <text>无限训练</text>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="stack-tight">
          <view class="secondary-button" bindtap="handleActivate">
            <text>{{isPaying ? '支付处理中...' : '确认支付并开通'}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="ghost-button" bindtap="handleClosePay">
            <text>取消</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
